<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Congratulations on your new pet, {{petName}}!</h1>
        <p>You have just made a furry friend for life.</p>
        <p>Amount Paid: ${{amount}}</p>
        <p>Thank you for choosing Proud Pete's Pet Emporium.</p>
        <p>We hope you and {{petName}} have many happy moments together.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to our team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Proud Pete's Pet Emporium Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>